name: DareNFT
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
DareNFT is the universal NFT 2.0 protocol for Digital Assets. 

The mainstream adoption of NFT depends on its ability to wholly reflect the benefits of digital assets and DareNFT has developed a suite of products that solve the current problems of NFT 1.0, which are: Unrecognized benefits between NFTs, Unrecognized relationship between NFT owners, and hidden risks of NFT Ownership.
